角析[真空]紫外光電子能譜儀: angle resolved ultraviolet photoelectron spectrometer {= ARUPS}

大氣壓離子化質譜儀 {API-MS}: atmospheric pressure ionization mass spectrometer {= API-MS}

揮發性有機化合物[不鏽鋼筒]自動採樣器: auto volatile organic compound canister sampler

愛迪生蓄電池[組] {鐵鎳蓄電池[組]}: Edison storage battery {Edison battery; iron-nickel accumulator}

電子順磁共振[光]譜儀: electron paramagnetic resonance spectrometer {= EPR spectrometer}

X射線能量散布分析儀: energy dispersive X-ray spectrometer {= EDS; EDX}

化學分析電子[能]譜儀: ESCA {electron spectroscopy for chemical analysis} spectrometer

誘導電位記錄及刺激器: event-related potential recorder and stimulator {= ERP recorder and stimulator}

極低頻電磁場檢測儀: extremely low frequency electromagnetic field monitor

快速原子撞擊質譜儀: fast atom bombardment mass spectrometer {= FAB-MS}

場發射掃描電子顯微鏡: field emission scanning electron microscope {= FESEM}

場發射穿透電子顯微鏡: field emission transmission electron microscope {= FETEM}

氣相層析核磁共振譜儀: gas chromatograph-nuclear magnetic resonance spectrometer {= GC-NMR}

高解析電子能量損失頻譜儀: high resolution electron energy loss spectrometer {= HREELS}

電感電容電阻測試儀: Inductance (L), Capacitance (C), and Resistance (R) meter {= LCR meter}

感應耦合電漿質譜儀；感應偶合電漿質譜儀: inductively coupled plasma mass spectrometer {= ICP-MS}

雷射: light amplification by stimulated emission of radiation {= laser}

金屬表面電漿子及二次諧波產生器: metal surface plasmon and second harmonic generator

邁射: microwave amplification by stimulated emission of radiation {= maser}

移動絲氫焰游離偵檢器: moving wire hydrogen flame ionization detector

多[路]徑傅立葉轉換紅外光譜儀: multi-path Fourier transform infrared spectrometer {= multi-path FTIR}

全波減光鏡: ND filter {neutral density filter; neutral filter}

釹：釔鋁石榴石雷射；摻釹釔鋁石榴石雷射: Nd:YAG laser {neodymium-doped yttrium aluminium garnet laser}
